{"tid":801871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵行李限制為長、闊、高合共不能超過130厘米  大型行李須託運並不能同時到埗","createTime":"2018-09-01T04:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T05:09:15.000Z","uid":136994,"like":177,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"520ca4433040c1c675abe4d504ab092f913b8fd5","tid":801871,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:09:55.000Z","msg":"高鐵規定乘客只可攜帶小型行李，大型行李便要託運。但有意見指託運的行李未能與乘客同時到埗，港鐵表示正與承辦商商討。  <br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成表示：「因內地高鐵網絡的要求，長、闊、高合共是不能超過130厘米，所以我們是必須要執行，假如旅客有溝通方面等，他不覺意帶了大型行李，我們必須要找渠道幫他們處理。我們找了服務承辦商提供行李運送服務，至於細節在跟服務商開始落實，當有這方面消息會再和大家公布。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港鐵正一on撚柒鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地鐵行李限制都有長、闊、高合共不能超過170厘米啦 <br />\n130cm 大小小嘅喼就超過咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有乜可能高鐵嘅規定仲緊過地鐵㗎<br />\n不過咁，我強烈要求港鐵要嚴厲執法<br />\n畀班港豬廢老五毛感受一下高鐵有幾咁方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"3f55950583c6174b1a847338ab788cd62d0718e3","tid":801871,"uid":17646,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"唔可以同時到,咁不如我搭飛機啦<br />\n等你到左又要再分行李係邊架車"},{"pid":"6f2c5723d49c489878dfa5c090fd6fc2ce50b92e","tid":801871,"uid":37596,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:11:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那高鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b896eca132afd0e8cdb49fd9d7dc812553a9d3d","tid":801871,"uid":51747,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"3f55950583c6174b1a847338ab788cd62d0718e3","tid":801871,"uid":17646,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"唔可以同時到,咁不如我搭飛機啦<br />\n等你到左又要再分行李係邊架車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"其實託運可能係用順豐嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc7f394110104d2b0b24135211ba8e51d5f44f0","tid":801871,"uid":195944,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚴格執行 邊個行李大小超過規定就一定要拒載！！"},{"pid":"2cf3da889561608440ee1c7e0276ece0176d01b8","tid":801871,"uid":36441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0b896eca132afd0e8cdb49fd9d7dc812553a9d3d","tid":801871,"uid":51747,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"3f55950583c6174b1a847338ab788cd62d0718e3","tid":801871,"uid":17646,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"唔可以同時到,咁不如我搭飛機啦<br />\n等你到左又要再分行李係邊架車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"其實託運可能係用順豐嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"諗下好 分分鐘用中通果啲集運<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdc13dc239e9eacc9a611fe255d23003d15f102","tid":801871,"uid":37586,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:18:51.000Z","msg":"見識少,鐵路收行李運費係咪香港領先全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n特登整細個限制,再收係運費,又羸<br />\n下次學飛機咁,計重量每KG計,收錢收到手軟,千億回本不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b35fbdbe8c44e8b057310929e19f06b3a33c351","tid":801871,"uid":42215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bbdc13dc239e9eacc9a611fe255d23003d15f102","tid":801871,"uid":37586,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:18:51.000Z","msg":"見識少,鐵路收行李運費係咪香港領先全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n特登整細個限制,再收係運費,又羸<br />\n下次學飛機咁,計重量每KG計,收錢收到手軟,千億回本不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/t